This package contains the classes related to the appointment models.

This package contains the enums used in the appointment module.

This package contains the common base classes that are used by other packages.

This package contains classes that are used to generate unique IDs for the system.

This package contains the classes for related to the inventory.

This package contains the controller classes called managers.

This package contains the prescription model and its repository.

This package contains the boundary classes for the system.
hms.system.service
This package contains the boundary-manager classes called services.

This package contains the classes that are responsible for the user interface of the application.

This package contains the classes that represent the user models.

This package contains the repository classes for the user models.

This package contains utility classes that are used in the application.
